{"tid":1439315,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"真。香港人打經濟貿易戰，多戰線重擊香港政府要害","createTime":"2019-08-10T05:20:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-10T12:35:10.000Z","uid":297350,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1e2bc8cca818162cab1c4baa1d93d22a0310bf9c","tid":1439315,"uid":297350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:20:23.000Z","msg":"首先多謝大家咁熱烈咁推POST<br />\nP牌嘅小弟真係受寵若驚<br />\n<br />\n點解林鄭絕口不提機場一切運動？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1437912\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1437912</a><br />\n<br />\n個運動嚟到呢一刻<br />\n眼見勇武嘅風險日高<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">究極和理非表示 <br />\n真。香港人 一定要用實際行動<br />\n打貿易戰</span></span><br />\n<br />\n古語有云，虛則實之，實則虛之<br />\n林鄭表明打經濟牌<br />\n要以民生作為人質要脅<br />\n要 真。香港人停止抗爭<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">翻查歷史<br />\n每個國家亡國前必定經歷嘅係<br />\n民不聊生，經濟崩壞</span></span><br />\n<br />\n點解林鄭要強調示威者會搞亂經濟<br />\n係因為<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">經濟穩定<br />\n民心先會穩定</span></span><br />\n藍絲人民先至會將矛頭直指示威者<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">一旦<br />\n係一旦</span></span><br />\n經濟真係衰退衰落<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就算政府點指摘示威者都好<br />\n民眾都係會將民生搞不好歸咎於政府</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2003年50萬人上街<br />\n就係因為政府無法搞好經濟<br />\n2000年IT泡沫爆破後<br />\n經濟一直走下坡<br />\n管治困難都係由2000開始發酵<br />\n到2003年終於大爆發</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我哋一定要多管齊下<br />\n全面開展經濟貿易戰線<br />\n要政府明白民眾推動嘅巨輪係勢不可當<br />\n一旦巨輪推動了，要停下絕不容易<br />\n<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">星期五 星期日 罷買 減少外出用餐 制約消費</span></span><br />\n全面杯葛親共商場、餐廳、服飾<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">推動機場空管人員罷工 和你飛全面行動支持兄弟</span></span><br />\n 推倒貿易，令GDP急降<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 叉住政府條頸</span></span><br />\n<br />\n3 <span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">稅務不合作運動</span></span><br />\n 用各種方法<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">反對評稅 延遲繳交稅項</span></span><br />\n<br />\n4 <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">宣揚不買樓保平安</span></span><br />\n 各種印花稅是政府主要收入來源<br />\n 當預測樓價大跌，政府收入來源將大幅減少<br />\n<br />\n記得<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">經濟貿易戰絕對唔需要擔心失民心</span></span><br />\n若果政府見到經濟勢色唔對都唔回應<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">後果自負嘅必然係政府</span></span><br />\n因為人民最終一定係會歸咎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府唔回應訴求才引起經濟雪崩</span></span><br />\n<br />\n中間失去少量民心只係陣痛期<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">絕對唔洗驚</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">到經濟入寒冬時<br />\n民眾自然會將矛頭直指政府</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"e4eb06480c86d158c92cf0479bc578f8807e2658","tid":1439315,"uid":295639,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:23:49.000Z","msg":"戒煙"},{"pid":"6e45abfadda37ea5ca7bbe6d026b3590c5ef29f6","tid":1439315,"uid":156092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T05:26:13.000Z","msg":"罷買會work ge!!"},{"pid":"336c8b7b5bb13e2582a052ee96b321fc92c084a0","tid":1439315,"uid":297350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T08:55:20.000Z","msg":"自推 1/10"},{"pid":"2b74667f76399fc3bd52be0eb205f0c8191e0d07","tid":1439315,"uid":297350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-10T12:35:10.000Z","msg":"再推"}]}